name: aMule for Windows
body:
## Current release
### Version 2.3.2 release 1
The release is built with Visual Studio 2013 and is based on the following:
* aMule 2.3.2
* boost 1.62.0
* Crypto++ 5.6.1
* GeoIP 1.4.6
* wxWidgets 2.8.12
